title: Cozy spacious single family house near all things

posting_body: ['This cozy one level single family house features 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, livingroom, dining and kitchen, laundry room, back covered porch and a concrete pad large enough for a basketball court.', 'A storage shad in the rear yard.', 'NO GARAGE.', 'Driveway parking.', 'Situated one block from Cupertino Downtown Main Street with numerous restaurants, grocery, banks, etc.', 'Minutes away from the Apple Spaceship Main Campus.', 'Within 1 mile from Cupertino High School, Warren E. Hyde Middle School and DJ Sedgewick Elementary School.', 'Easy access to Lawrence Expressway, Highway 280, 85, 101 and 880.', 'Seeking a responsible family to  enjoy this house.', 'Tenants to pay for all utilities and yard maintenance.']
